00:07:33.870 --> 00:07:40.800 align:middle line:84%
>> In the '60s, in March
6, 1961 to be exact,

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:46.600 align:middle line:84%
Timothy Leary gave me psilocybin
and it changed my life.

00:07:46.600 --> 00:07:52.080 align:middle line:84%
It changed my life in the sense
that it undercut the models

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:54.700 align:middle line:90%
I had of who I thought I was.

00:07:54.700 --> 00:07:57.030 align:middle line:84%
All as socialization
and child development

00:07:57.030 --> 00:08:01.080 align:middle line:84%
that had left me with a
very strong somebodyness,

00:08:01.080 --> 00:08:02.080 align:middle line:90%
it cut that out.

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:03.840 align:middle line:84%
And, of course, there
was fear in losing

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:06.120 align:middle line:90%
that familiar identity.

00:08:06.120 --> 00:08:08.190 align:middle line:84%
But there was
always also, wonder.

00:08:08.190 --> 00:08:11.340 align:middle line:84%
Because I touched
a place in myself.

00:08:11.340 --> 00:08:15.570 align:middle line:10%
It was behind all
my social roles.

00:08:15.570 --> 00:08:20.610 align:middle line:10%
And it was-- it was a presence.

00:08:20.610 --> 00:08:27.990 align:middle line:84%
Instead of being good or this
or that or achiever or anything,

00:08:27.990 --> 00:08:31.110 align:middle line:84%
I experienced a place in
myself where I just say, I am.

00:08:31.110 --> 00:08:32.430 align:middle line:90%
Not I am this or I am that.

00:08:32.430 --> 00:08:33.960 align:middle line:90%
Just I am.

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:37.260 align:middle line:84%
And I think it
preoccupied me because it

00:08:37.260 --> 00:08:40.320 align:middle line:90%
felt like it was my true being.

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:41.850 align:middle line:90%
And I felt like I was gypped.

00:08:41.850 --> 00:08:45.640 align:middle line:84%
I was gypping myself not
to have access to that.

00:08:45.640 --> 00:08:49.560 align:middle line:84%
So I did what many others of you
did and other people did, was I

00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:56.338 align:middle line:84%
tried every chemical possibility
to try to stabilize that state.

00:08:56.338 --> 00:08:58.380 align:middle line:84%
If you took this, and then
followed it with this,

00:08:58.380 --> 00:08:59.922 align:middle line:84%
