foot it would work, see.

00:09:08.100 --> 00:09:09.705 align:middle line:84%
And I still came
down, and I kept

00:09:09.705 --> 00:09:11.580 align:middle line:84%
coming down, and coming
down, and coming down

00:09:11.580 --> 00:09:12.930 align:middle line:90%
