00:09:12.930 --> 00:09:15.940 align:middle line:84%
Through hundreds and hundreds
and hundreds of exploration.

00:09:15.940 --> 00:09:19.620 align:middle line:90%


00:09:19.620 --> 00:09:24.000 align:middle line:84%
And then I went to India and
I met Maharaj Ji, my guru.

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:26.130 align:middle line:84%
