who didn't come down.

00:09:26.130 --> 00:09:34.570 align:middle line:90%


00:09:34.570 --> 00:09:38.320 align:middle line:10%
What I experienced at that time
of meeting that man-- in fact,

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:42.970 align:middle line:10%
within those first few
minutes of meeting--

00:09:42.970 --> 00:09:50.250 align:middle line:10%
was the experience of surrender,
which was no surrender.

00:09:50.250 --> 00:09:54.570 align:middle line:84%
In other words, I didn't
begrudgingly give up my ego.

00:09:54.570 --> 00:09:56.610 align:middle line:84%
It was as if I came
home to the place

00:09:56.610 --> 00:09:59.730 align:middle line:90%
where I no longer needed it.

00:09:59.730 --> 00:10:02.585 align:middle line:84%
They took over my complete
life at that point.

00:10:02.585 --> 00:10:03.960 align:middle line:84%
I didn't leave
that temple again,

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:06.870 align:middle line:84%
except to go to Delhi
once for seven months.

00:10:06.870 --> 00:10:10.150 align:middle line:84%
They took over my food,
my clothing, my training--

00:10:10.150 --> 00:10:10.950 align:middle line:90%
everything.

00:10:10.950 --> 00:10:14.160 align:middle line:90%
Never anybody asked or said.

00:10:14.160 --> 00:10:16.545 align:middle line:84%
It was all done from
then on from inside.

00:10:16.545 --> 00:10:19.680 align:middle line:90%


00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:24.180 align:middle line:84%
I learned about what
inside education is about.

00:10:24.180 --> 00:10:29.250 align:middle line:84%
And this man was
at the place where

00:10:29.250 --> 00:10:33.870 align:middle line:84%
there was no other person
you were giving up to.

00:10:33.870 --> 00:10:38.970 align:middle line:84%
And everything I did from then
on was done with absolute joy.

00:10:38.970 --> 00:10:43.910 align:middle line:10%
There was no thing they could
ask of me that was too hard.

00:10:43.910 --> 00:10:48.020 align:middle line:10%
It was austerities
that we're not austere.

00:10:48.020 --> 00:10:53.690 align:middle line:84%
Because I was living
almost within this man.

00:10:53.690 --> 00:10:56.370 align:middle line:84%
For the first time, I understood
what the concept of a guru

00:10:56.370 --> 00:10:57.390 align:middle line:90%
was about.

00:10:57.390 --> 00:10:59.920 align:middle line:84%
See, a guru is your
doorway to God.

00:10:59.920 --> 00:11:01.820 align:middle line:90%
Your doorway to the beyond.

00:11:01.820 --> 00:11:05.150 align:middle line:84%
A guru is not just
a groovy teacher.

00:11:05.150 --> 00:11:05.990 align:middle line:90%
It's not a pundit.

00:11:05.990 --> 00:11:09.050 align:middle line:84%
It's not just a wise man
who can teach you things.

00:11:09.050 --> 00:11:16.280 align:middle line:84%
A guru is a spiritual
vehicle, an entrance way.

00:11:16.280 --> 00:11:17.270 align:middle line:90%
He's a pure mirror.

00:11:17.270 --> 00:11:18.590 align:middle line:90%
