00:42:50.740 --> 00:42:55.930 align:middle line:10%
Just experience that it was
grace, that that death allowed

00:42:55.930 --> 00:42:58.420 align:middle line:10%
you to waken for a moment.

00:42:58.420 --> 00:42:59.920 align:middle line:10%
Because the minute
you try to grab

00:42:59.920 --> 00:43:02.380 align:middle line:10%
onto the memory of
what it was, you're

00:43:02.380 --> 00:43:05.700 align:middle line:10%
just holding onto an
old dead butterfly.

00:43:05.700 --> 00:43:08.550 align:middle line:10%
So you go back to sleep and
then you'll wake up again.

00:43:08.550 --> 00:43:11.040 align:middle line:10%
