process at work.

00:43:13.590 --> 00:43:15.750 align:middle line:10%
You have to stand back
one step further and see

00:43:15.750 --> 00:43:18.000 align:middle line:10%
your whole life, the awakening
and the going to sleep,

00:43:18.000 --> 00:43:20.150 align:middle line:10%
all is awakening.

00:43:20.150 --> 00:43:22.760 align:middle line:10%
