where our destruction lies.

00:48:04.230 --> 00:48:07.200 align:middle line:84%
We've thought our way into
this peculiar situation, where

00:48:07.200 --> 00:48:10.980 align:middle line:84%
we were alienated from the
Earth and from each other,

00:48:10.980 --> 00:48:15.880 align:middle line:84%
and caught in greed, which
is a product of the mind.

00:48:15.880 --> 00:48:18.160 align:middle line:84%
And each of us must
be true to ourselves

00:48:18.160 --> 00:48:21.880 align:middle line:84%
to hear what is our
unique way through,

00:48:21.880 --> 00:48:26.050 align:middle line:84%
because if you get
phony wholly, it ends up

00:48:26.050 --> 00:48:28.235 align:middle line:90%
kicking you in the butt.

00:48:28.235 --> 00:48:29.735 align:middle line:84%
You've got to stay
true to yourself.

00:48:29.735 --> 00:48:32.830 align:middle line:90%


00:48:32.830 --> 00:48:36.670 align:middle line:84%
And as Chogyam Trungpa said
in his rascally way, he said,

00:48:36.670 --> 00:48:40.460 align:middle line:84%
"Enlightenment is the ego's
ultimate disappointment."

00:48:40.460 --> 00:48:41.740 align:middle line:90%
And that's the predicament.

00:48:41.740 --> 00:48:45.550 align:middle line:84%
You see the fact that
your spiritual journey

00:48:45.550 --> 00:48:48.340 align:middle line:84%
is an entirely different
ballgame than the one you

00:48:48.340 --> 00:48:49.180 align:middle line:90%
thought you were on.

00:48:49.180 --> 00:48:51.490 align:middle line:84%
It's a different path than
