00:48:51.490 --> 00:48:53.820 align:middle line:84%
And it's very hard to
make that transition.

00:48:53.820 --> 00:48:55.240 align:middle line:84%
And a lot of people
don't want to.

00:48:55.240 --> 00:48:57.940 align:middle line:84%
They want to take the power
