00:48:57.940 --> 00:49:01.450 align:middle line:90%
and make their life nice.

00:49:01.450 --> 00:49:03.990 align:middle line:84%
And there is a grief when
who you thought you were it

00:49:03.990 --> 00:49:05.020 align:middle line:90%
starts to disappear.

00:49:05.020 --> 00:49:12.880 align:middle line:90%


00:49:12.880 --> 00:49:16.240 align:middle line:84%
You can imagine a picture
frame in which there is

00:49:16.240 --> 00:49:18.205 align:middle line:90%
of a painting of a gray cloud.

00:49:18.205 --> 00:49:21.700 align:middle line:90%


00:49:21.700 --> 00:49:24.700 align:middle line:84%
But the painter made the
cloud bigger than the frame

00:49:24.700 --> 00:49:26.030 align:middle line:90%
that he had--

00:49:26.030 --> 00:49:26.830 align:middle line:90%
she had.

00:49:26.830 --> 00:49:30.610 align:middle line:84%
So what they did was they
cut a little off the edge,

00:49:30.610 --> 00:49:32.060 align:middle line:84%
and they just put
it in the frame

00:49:32.060 --> 00:49:34.843 align:middle line:84%
until all there is
is gray cloudiness,

00:49:34.843 --> 00:49:36.760 align:middle line:84%
because there's no edge
anymore to the clouds.

00:49:36.760 --> 00:49:39.307 align:middle line:84%
So all you have is
gray in a frame.

00:49:39.307 --> 00:49:41.140 align:middle line:84%
And you look at it and
you say, what's that?

00:49:41.140 --> 00:49:47.190 align:middle line:90%


