00:50:27.870 --> 00:50:30.550 align:middle line:90%
to give you that space.

00:50:30.550 --> 00:50:33.540 align:middle line:84%
And the minute there's
that spaciousness,

00:50:33.540 --> 00:50:37.380 align:middle line:90%
it's just another cloud.

00:50:37.380 --> 00:50:39.030 align:middle line:84%
You know what clouds
do in the sky?

00:50:39.030 --> 00:50:41.700 align:middle line:90%
They come and they go.

00:50:41.700 --> 00:50:49.880 align:middle line:90%


00:50:49.880 --> 00:50:52.480 align:middle line:10%
And then there
comes a period where

00:50:52.480 --> 00:50:56.140 align:middle line:10%
you've just gone through
enough, and the space starts--

00:50:56.140 --> 00:50:58.300 align:middle line:10%
that little blue sky
starts to develop.

00:50:58.300 --> 00:51:01.810 align:middle line:84%
And if you have a meditative
awareness, or just

00:51:01.810 --> 00:51:05.545 align:middle line:84%
that appreciation, you start
to identify with the blue sky

00:51:05.545 --> 00:51:06.420 align:middle line:90%
instead of the cloud.

00:51:06.420 --> 00:51:14.450 align:middle line:84%
You flicker at first, and
then you start to release.

00:51:14.450 --> 00:51:18.280 align:middle line:84%
And then comes the
time when you start

00:51:18.280 --> 00:51:22.750 align:middle line:84%
to realize you'd rather
be vulnerable and be hurt

00:51:22.750 --> 00:51:26.060 align:middle line:84%
than be living dead in
the dead, dead sense,

00:51:26.060 --> 00:51:28.700 align:middle line:90%
not in the living sense.

00:51:28.700 --> 00:51:30.020 align:middle line:90%
And you can't afford it.

00:51:30.020 --> 00:51:32.510 align:middle line:84%
And you start to open
again, and the whole cycle

00:51:32.510 --> 00:51:40.990 align:middle line:84%
starts again, until
finally, you start

00:51:40.990 --> 00:51:44.270 align:middle line:90%
to fall in love with love.

00:51:44.270 --> 00:51:49.210 align:middle line:90%


