00:53:54.520 --> 00:53:58.690 align:middle line:10%
with a certain kind of falseness
that comes out of our own fear.

00:53:58.690 --> 00:54:02.880 align:middle line:84%
When my mother, my
natural mother was dying,

00:54:02.880 --> 00:54:05.882 align:middle line:84%
