00:54:12.900 --> 00:54:15.910 align:middle line:84%
And I thought how bizarre
that a human being

00:54:15.910 --> 00:54:18.510 align:middle line:84%
is going through one of the
most profound transitions

00:54:18.510 --> 00:54:20.670 align:middle line:84%
in their life, and they're
surrounded completely

00:54:20.670 --> 00:54:22.500 align:middle line:90%
by deception?

00:54:22.500 --> 00:54:25.980 align:middle line:84%
Can you hear the pain of that,
that nobody could be straight

00:54:25.980 --> 00:54:28.710 align:middle line:84%
