>> Yeah, suppression of lack.

01:02:53.990 --> 01:02:57.620 align:middle line:84%
>> An abundance of
lack, so abundant.

01:02:57.620 --> 01:02:58.495 align:middle line:90%
>> Abundance of lack.

01:02:58.495 --> 01:03:02.540 align:middle line:90%


01:03:02.540 --> 01:03:04.905 align:middle line:84%
>> His Royal majesty,
the abundance of lack.

